Description: Wallpaper Engine integration for KDE Plasma 6
 A wallpaper plugin integrating Wallpaper Engine into KDE Plasma 6
 wallpaper settings. Supports Scene (2D), Web, and Video wallpapers.
 .
 This is a maintained fork with native C++ file operations, fixed
 KDE 6.5+ theme reactivity, and full Plasma 6 / Qt6 support.
 .
 Requires Wallpaper Engine installed on Steam and subscribed Workshop
 wallpapers.
